name: Round A (Ronda)
description:
Round_A or Ronda is an activity in my country that gathers a village or a small area to protect the area. Usually it consists of fathers, and the activity is carried out in rotation until morning. most of them are happy with the activity because they can joke and play cards. sometimes it is interspersed with watching the situation rotate to the boundary.
